Description: 
        Energy
        ~~~~~~
        
        Energy system for social games such as FarmVille or The Sims Social.
        
        >>> energy = Energy(10, recovery_interval=10)
        >>> energy
        <Energy 10/10>
        >>> energy.use()
        9
        >>> energy
        <Energy 9/10 recover in 00:09>
        
